The magic really happens in the useSupamachine hook, which deterministically manages auth state via a standard reducer pattern.

So in the most basic scenario, all you need to do is:

• Give useSupamachine your Supabase client

• Provide a basic loadContext function that gets the user’s profile

• Wrap your app in <SupamachineProvider>

• Get auth state from useSupamachine and use it to declaratively render your app.

